text: "FM (No Static at All)" is a 1978 song by Steely Dan and is the title track the 1978 movie FM. It went to number 1 in Spain, number 19 in Canada and New Zealand, number 22 in the United States, number 49 in the United Kingdom and number 87 in Australia. It won a Grammy Award for Best Engineered Recording, Non-Classical in 1979. ==References== Category:1978 songs Category:Steely Dan songs
